Patricia F. Baker, Individually and as Executrix of Edward C. Baker, Deceased, Respondent-Appellant, v Sport-service Corporation, Appellant-Respondent. (Appeal No. 2.)

Appeals unanimously dismissed without costs (see, Hughes v *655Nussbaumer, Clarke & Velzy, 140 AD2d 988; see also, CPLR 5501 [a] [1]). (Appeals from Order of Supreme Court, Erie County, Fudeman, J. — Negligence.) Present — Callahan, J. P., Doerr, Green, Pine and Lowery, JJ.
